      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "This gives me this error <code>Java HotSpot(TM) 64-Bit Server VM warning: Ignoring option MaxPermSize; support was removed in 8.0 WARNING: An illegal reflective access operation has occurred WARNING: Illegal reflective access by org.eclipse.osgi.internal.baseadaptor.BaseStorage (file:&#47;usr&#47;lib&#47;eclipse&#47;plugins&#47;org.eclipse.osgi_3.8.1.dist.j&zwnj;&#8203;ar) to method java.net.URLClassLoader.addURL(java.net.URL) WARNING: Please consider reporting this to the maintainers of org.eclipse.osgi.internal.baseadaptor.BaseStorage</code>  How can I solve it?"
