    "question_id" : 10165693,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>A possibly more generic method is to:</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>install non-headless version of the openjdk, </li>\n<li>install, run and close eclipse.</li>\n<li>uninstall the openjdk</li>\n<li>install oracle's JDK</li>\n</ul>\n"
