    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>I installed the JDK 32 bit because of that I am getting the errors. After installing JDK 64 bit <a href=\"http://www.oracle.com/technetwork/java/javase/downloads/jdk8-downloads-2133151.html\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">http://www.oracle.com/technetwork/java/javase/downloads/jdk8-downloads-2133151.html</a>\njdk-8u131-linux-x64.tar.gz(please download the 64 version)\nand download  64 bit \"eclipse-inst-linux64.tar.gz\".</p>\n"
